It also has a meeting room for up to 90 people.
Many of the major events held in Hunter's Creek occur at Osprey Park.
These include the Hunter's Creek Women's Association's Bunny in the Park and Fall Festival, and the HCCA Recreation and Special Events Department's Independence Day Celebration and Halloween (Hunter's Creep Nights) haunted house and hayride.
